{
  "stem": "7624.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my-- first of all, may I come back to when I came to the States, here?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in Hartford, and I came here to Miami, and I started to work here in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the summertime, I was in the Catskill Mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked there for six months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in 1950, I got a letter from the draft-- draftees, and Uncle Sam said, I need you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1939, when I was outside here, Miami Beach, he didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Korean War was on, and he drafted me in the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I passed my interpreter test as German and French, but I was sent to Korea.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I was lucky there again, because I was mostly stationed in Japan.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after, I worked as a baker, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even I made some good cake for General Mark Clark, and he asked me if I would like to be his pastry chef there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I have to be more many years in the army [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wanted to be free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came back to the-- out of the army, and I came back to Florida.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I started to work-- there was a job open as a helper at the Fontainebleau Hotel when they opened up in 1954, and I took that job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked there for 12 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the meantime, I was always in touch with this organization.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a wonderful woman who's from Russia, Mme.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Azure, she was like a mother to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to visit her one time, and she said, would you like to be a pen pal with a girl from France?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She would like to be with somebody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, certainly.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
